Package org.eclipse.ecf.telephony.call

Interface Summary
ICallSession Contract for interacting with an arbitrary call session.
ICallSessionContainerAdapter Call session container entry point adapter.
ICallSessionListener Listener for receiving call session events from remotes.
ICallSessionRequestListener Listener for call session creation requests.
 

Class Summary
CallSessionErrorDetails A type-safe enum class to represent error details for an ICallSession.
CallSessionFailureReason A class to represent the reason for a failure.
CallSessionState Type-safe enumeration class to represent call session state information.
 

Exception Summary
CallException Exception thrown by Call API calls.
